## 封装加载图片的promise  
```js
let loadImg = (src)=>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        // write your code here
    })
}
```

student_answer:
let loadImg = (src)=>{
  return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
    let img = new Image();
    img.src=src
    img.onload =function(){
      resolve(img)
    }
  })
}
loadImg('./img.png').then((res)=>{
  document.body.appendChild(res)
})
